'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 61''' is the sixty-first issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[April 25]], [[1979]]. This is the first issue to start printing US stories in three parts instead of two, making room in the book for more pages than usual from the other non-''Star Wars'' stories.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 27|''Star Wars'' (1977) 27]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"Micronauts Part 5: A hunting we will go!" (continuation)
*"Tales of the Watcher: The thing from Planet X"

